```{r}
library(ggplot2)
library(plotly)
library(tidyverse)
aisc2024 <- read_csv("aisc2024.csv")
plot <- aisc2024 |> ggplot(aes(x = tempo)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 10)
ggplotly(plot)
```
